<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I found the answer to this question myself, it is explained in the text a little way into the book. It is intended to serve as an elaboration on the p<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I found the answer to this question myself, it is explained in the text a little way into the book. It is intended to serve as an elaboration on the protagonist's personality. I didn't find the explanation particularly credible or satisfactory, though.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
